                                      SERVER "name"

        and, optionally, one or more of the following switches:

|                                     /CLUSTER-NODE:cluster-node-name
                                      /PAUSE:nnnn
                                      /REPEAT-COUNT:nnnn
                                      /STOP

        or, optionally, the following argument:

                                      alignment-filespec




