                           specifies the destination to receive IBM  card
                           punch  output.  This is valid only if node has
                           been defined as an  SNA-WORKSTATION  with  the
                                                               __________                           DEFINE   NODE  command.   See  the  DECnet/SNA
                           _______ ______ ___ _____ ______ ___ __________                           TOPS-20 Remote Job Entry User's and Operator's
