                                      AVAILABLE
                                      DOMESTIC
                                      DUMPABLE
                                      EXCLUSIVE
                                      FOREIGN
                                      IGNORED
                                      NODUMPABLE
                                      REGULATED
                                      SHARED
                                      UNAVAILABLE
                                      UNREGULATED
|  
|       optionally followed by the switch:
|  
|                                     /CLUSTER-NODE:cluster-node-name


