        or

              ________ ________________             $^ECREATE SQM:<HOGAN><RET>
             [Old]
               ________ __________             $$PASSWORD JOHNQ<RET>
               _____             $$<RET>
             $

        Also, see Hint under PASSWORD subcommand,  described  later,  for
        another way of changing a password.



