            _________  __  _____   ________  ___ ________ _____ ______ __            installed  on  SYS:.   However,  the database files cannot be
            _________ _____ ________  ______ ____ _____ ________ __  ____            converted until tonight.  Please wait until tomorrow to  make
            ___ _____________            new entries.<RET>

            The message appears on the receiving terminals as:

            [From OPERATOR on line 17:
            Your new short-ship tracking program is installed on
